OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FWATCH: A group of Chagos Islanders,
OL,8,Fstaying in temporary accommodation in
OL,9,FCrawley, fear they could be made
OL,10,Fhomeless, as Kit Bradshaw reports.
OL,12,FDozens of people with family
OL,13,Fconnections to the Chagos Islands fear
OL,14,Fthey are about be made homeless in
OL,15,FCrawley.
