OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe group, from Mauritius, obtained UK
OL,8,Fpassports through a citizenship scheme
OL,9,Fand have been staying at Northgate
OL,10,FCommunity Centre in the town since
OL,11,Farriving at Gatwick Airport two weeks
OL,12,Fago.
OL,14,FChagos Islanders and their direct
OL,15,Fdescendants are entitled to British
OL,16,Fcitizenship after they were expelled
OL,17,Fby the UK from their homeland in the
OL,18,F1960s and 70s to make way for a US
OL,19,Fmilitary base.
