OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FAlthough Crawley Borough Council
OL,8,Foffered emergency accommodation to
OL,9,Fsome, the remainder did not qualify,
OL,10,Fand had nowhere else to go.
OL,12,FOfficials had expected the rest centre
OL,13,Fto be open for 24-48 hours, to allow
OL,14,Ffor those affected to make alternative
OL,15,Farrangements. It has now been running
OL,16,Ffor more than two weeks.
OL,18,FThe local authority said the centre
OL,19,Fwill close on Thursday, as they do not
OL,20,Fhave the resources to keep running it
OL,21,Fwith the election next week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
