OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe borough council said it has
OL,8,Fapproached the government for support,
OL,9,Fonly to be told that it is "a local
OL,10,Fproblem".
OL,12,FIn a statement, Crawley Borough
OL,13,FCouncil said: "On 10 June 2024, 52 UK
OL,14,Fcitizens of Chagossian descent arrived
OL,15,Ffrom Mauritius. They were joined by a
OL,16,Ffurther 25 people who had previously
OL,17,Fmade the same journey. These
OL,18,Findividuals had obtained UK passports
OL,19,Fthrough the Chagossian British
OL,20,FOverseas Territories Citizenship
OL,21,Fscheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
