OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"On arrival none of these individuals
OL,8,Fhad plans in place for accommodation.
OL,9,FFollowing assessment 37 individuals
OL,10,Fremained without a place to stay, but
OL,11,Falso with no right to emergency
OL,12,Faccommodation. Given the numbers
OL,13,Finvolved and the lack of other support
OL,14,Favailable, we took the decision to
OL,15,Fopen a rest centre on safety grounds...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
