OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"With the general election next week,
OL,8,Fwe do not have the staffing resources
OL,9,Fto be able to continue this effort,
OL,10,Fand run the election at the same time.
OL,11,FAccordingly we have approached
OL,12,Frelevant government departments for
OL,13,Fsupport, but they have insisted this
OL,14,Fis a local problem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
