OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"We have reluctantly therefore had to
OL,8,Finform those using the centre that it
OL,9,Fwill now need to close. We continue to
OL,10,Ftry and provide advice and guidance to
OL,11,Fthose in the rest centre in the
OL,12,Fmeantime, so they are fully aware of
OL,13,Fother support available."
OL,15,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,16,FUK Government is engaging with Crawley
OL,17,FBorough Council as it works to assist
OL,18,Fnew arrivals.
