OL,3,CChagos Islanders 'terrified for
OL,4,Cfuture' as Crawley Council shuts rest
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"In 2022, the UK Government created a
OL,8,Fnew route for Chagossians to become
OL,9,FBritish citizens, free of charge, and
OL,10,Fto build their future in the UK should
OL,11,Fthey wish to.
OL,13,F"The UK Government has published
OL,14,Fguidance for Chagossians moving to the
OL,15,FUK, which sets out their rights and
OL,16,Fresponsibilities as British citizens.
OL,17,FThis includes making their own
OL,18,Faccommodation arrangements before they
OL,19,Ftravel."
